Author: SmileIsKey
Text: You shouldnt eat this! You should look this this! This is unhealthy for you! Omg I barely ate todayyy how random. Have you tried fasting? it does wonders! Omg I'm so fat, I ate a cake and need to go to the gym now, I'm such a fat bitch teehee  These small comments before would never have lowered down my mood, but now actively trigger me.
